hey tom, was going through an archive of twokinds images and saw a few things of characters with golfclubs
do you remember what those were for?
Golfclubs are used to play golf with. They hit the ball, and the ball goes into a hole in the ground some distance away.
thus disqualifying golf as a sport
The real reason is because in 2009 I went to what was technically my first comic convention.
And the theme of the year was golf. They paid my way, and just asked me to draw my characters holding golf clubs.
That's great, I'm just going through some youtube videos and some forums.
